//store.steampowered.com/app/530711/Dead_by_Daylight__The_Halloween_Chapter"},{"category":1,"url":"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/chapter2/"}]},{"id":76222,"name":"Dead by Daylight - Of Flesh and Mud Chapter","slug":"dead-by-daylight-of-flesh-and-mud-chapter","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dead-by-daylight-of-flesh-and-mud-chapter","created_at":1511472272534,"updated_at":1511472288255,"summary":"\"Of Flesh and Mud is the third Chapter for Dead by Daylight. Prepare for dark hexes and flesh made out of mud and decay, if you dare enter Backwater Swamp and live through the horror it brings. A new killer - The Hag - awaits you in the waterland area and you will meet a new survivor: Ace Visconti. \n \nA hag driven to madness by being devoured alive piece by piece. A survivor that believes luck is always on his side. A wetland with scorched shacks, an eerie mud maze and a rusting boat graveyard lays ahead of you, so tread carefully. \n \nOf Flesh and Mud is the brand new Chapter for Dead by Daylight and it includes a new Killer, a new Survivor and a map.\"","popularity":1.666666666666667,"game":18866,"tags":[1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[1260],"publishers":[12898],"category":1,"player_perspectives":[1,2],"game_modes":[1,2,3],"keywords":[541],"themes":[1,19,23],"first_release_date":1481155200000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1481155200000,"region":8,"human":"2016-Dec-08","y":2016,"m":12}],"videos":[{"name":"Teaser","video_id":"hkuETjoU6GM"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gsyzyohgadknj6qcuwrc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gsyzyohgadknj6qcuwrc","width":414,"height":311},"websites":[{"category":13,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/554381/Dead_by_Daylight__Of_Flesh_and_Mud_Chapter"},{"category":1,"url":"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/chapter3/"}]},{"id":76223,"name":"Dead by Daylight - Spark of Madness Chapter","slug":"dead-by-daylight-spark-of-madness-chapter","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dead-by-daylight-spark-of-madness-chapter","created_at":1511472608419,"updated_at":1511472617301,"summary":"\"Spark of Madness is a Chapter for Dead by Daylight. It holds the darkest and most experimental form of treatment - where health is not the goal, just madness. The Doctor will see you now, whether you want to or not. The only glimpse of hope is a young girl, one who never gives up and always finds a way. \n \nTreatment in progress... \n \nInformation is power. \nEverything is allowed. \nIntelligence is a weapon that must be thwarted. \nThis doctor will never stop, treatments will never be too experimental. \nA young girl who is in it to win, no matter what the game or the rules. \nA research institution that slowly turns into a prison. \n \nThe Spark of Madness Chapter includes a new Killer, a Survivor and a Map.\"","popularity":2.0,"game":18866,"tags":[1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[1260],"publishers":[12898],"category":1,"player_perspectives":[1,2],"game_modes":[1,2,3],"keywords":[541],"themes":[1,19,23],"first_release_date":1494460800000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1494460800000,"region":8,"human":"2017-May-11","y":2017,"m":5}],"videos":[{"name":"Trailer","video_id":"2b5_5CKa1nc"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/elf8kuxolmipaflrdgxw.jpg","cloudinary_id":"elf8kuxolmipaflrdgxw","width":374,"height":308},"websites":[{"category":13,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/582600/Dead_by_Daylight__Spark_of_Madness_Chapter"},{"category":1,"url":"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/chapter4/"}]},{"id":76224,"name":"Dead by Daylight - A Lullaby for the Dark Chapter","slug":"dead-by-daylight-a-lullaby-for-the-dark-chapter","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dead-by-daylight-a-lullaby-for-the-dark-chapter","created_at":1511472857846,"updated_at":1511472887785,"summary":"\"A Lullaby for the Dark is a free Chapter for Dead by Daylight. Welcome to the other side of Mother Nature. A disturbing side where survival surpasses cannibalism and ends up in solitude. The Huntress will never miss her mark, she will track you, capture you and kill you. Hopefully a former rugby star might bring her down...if he doesn’t get lost in the Red Forest. \n \nForest of the damned \n \nSurvival is all. \nThere are no limits to what one abandoned child will do to make it through the day, year after year after year. Meat holds no face when it’s placed above a fire to be cooked. All she seeks is shelter and a long-lost mother that nature took away. Her simple cottage is all that is left - a mad girl’s paradise in a forsaken forest. Might Mr. King stand a chance against the forces of nature...once it unleashes The Huntress? \n \nA Lullaby for the Dark is a new Chapter for Dead by Daylight. It includes a new Killer, a Survivor and a Map.\"","popularity":1.666666666666667,"game":18866,"tags":[1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[1260],"publishers":[12898],"category":1,"player_perspectives":[1,2],"game_modes":[1,2,3],"keywords":[541],"themes":[1,19,23],"first_release_date":1501113600000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1501113600000,"region":8,"human":"2017-Jul-27","y":2017,"m":7}],"videos":[{"name":"Trailer","video_id":"9sXTC-uzjWM"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wb2lm2yncuen2sja3bkl.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wb2lm2yncuen2sja3bkl","width":720,"height":293},"websites":[{"category":13,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/661770/Dead_by_Daylight__A_Lullaby_for_the_Dark_Chapter"},{"category":1,"url":"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/chapter5/"}]},{"id":76225,"name":"Dead by Daylight - Leatherface","slug":"dead-by-daylight-leatherface","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dead-by-daylight-leatherface","created_at":1511473106528,"updated_at":1511473122777,"summary":"\"Leatherface is a Character DLC for Dead by Daylight. \n \nThis is slaughter in its purest form. A kind of slaughter driven by a pure need of flesh. Leatherface won’t fail and he won’t stop. As the chainsaw starts, you know what is coming. Pain and fear in a combination of panic as you understand that death isn’t the end. You will also end up on someone’s plate. \n \nAs the saw starts... \nWhat happens when the body grows but the mind can’t keep up? A child’s fears and anxiety, but trapped inside a fully grown man’s body. A furious body wielding a chainsaw? Someone who knows what happens as you disobey your family. What happens if anyone finds out what’s in the stew. \n \nLeatherface is not only the skin clad maniac with a disturbed mind. He seeks acceptance and appreciation. He’s learned the hard way and was molded to what he now is. A watchdog, a guardian, a blind gate keeper who never questions. And all problems can be solved with his chainsaw.\"","popularity":1.666666666666667,"game":18866,"tags":[1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[1260],"publishers":[12898],"category":1,"player_perspectives":[1,2],"game_modes":[1,2,3],"keywords":[541],"themes":[1,19,23],"first_release_date":1505347200000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1505347200000,"region":8,"human":"2017-Sep-14","y":2017,"m":9}],"videos":[{"name":"Gameplay video","video_id":"SyqgEK0CEVE"},{"name":"Trailer","video_id":"agq3D3J80io"},{"name":"Teaser","video_id":"YiGsh8RjAt0"}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ek4ycronubldtaylmhfg.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ek4ycronubldtaylmhfg","width":765,"height":243},"websites":[{"category":13,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/700280/Dead_by_Daylight__Leatherface"},{"category":1,"url":"http://www.deadbydaylight.com/chapter6/"}]},{"id":76226,"name":"Dead by Daylight - A Nightmare on Elm Street","slug":"dead-by-daylight-a-nightmare-on-elm-street","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/dead-by-daylight-a-nightmare-on-elm-street","created_at":1511473422932,"updated_at":1511473453318,"summary":"\"A Nightmare on Elm Street is a brand new Chapter for Dead by Daylight. \n \nThere are boogey men, an