e what they want to hear in order to advance your Reputation. \n* Carefully manage your social calendar to make sure you attend all the right parties without stretching yourself too thin and becoming exhausted. \n* Acquire and choose from dozens of outfits based on actual fashion plates and paintings from pre-revolutionary France. Wear these outfits to impress members of the five factions. \n* Seduce powerful individuals throughout France and manipulate them in order to solidify your power. \n* Increase your reputation with the five factions to unlock new bonuses and abilities. \n* A breathtaking soundtrack by award winning game composer, John Robert Matz! \n* Randomly generated world is different every time you play, as is the outcome of the revolution. \n* Uncover the mystery of Yvette's lost lover, Armand. \n* Become enemies with screeching harpies and chauvinistic boors, then drive them to social ruin! \n* Carefully observe the political winds and make sure you end up on the winning side of history.","popularity":4.0,"games":[2015,7440,24512,55036,13189,18623,236,27725,26917,19297],"tags":[22,268435458,1073741828],"developers":[13964],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"themes":[22],"genres":[2],"first_release_date":1546214400000,"pulse_count":2,"platforms":[6,14],"release_dates":[{"category":6,"platform":6,"date":1546214400000,"region":8,"human":"2018-Q4","y":2018,"m":12},{"category":6,"platform":14,"date":1546214400000,"region":8,"human":"2018-Q4","y":2018,"m":12}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/xtvpi9yszi3qtbc9hky3.jpg","cloudinary_id":"xtvpi9yszi3qtbc9hky3","width":1000,"height":563},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/k1ph6l3ybj2dfy8wezxl.jpg","cloudinary_id":"k1ph6l3ybj2dfy8wezxl","width":1000,"height":563},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zrqciqasnaf4kx6j5crr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zrqciqasnaf4kx6j5crr","width":1000,"height":563},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image